    "text": "Defending Americans from Authoritarian Digital Currencies Act\n\nThis bill prohibits app stores in the United States from carrying or supporting any app that allows transactions using the Chinese government's Digital Currency Electronic Payment system (e-CNY). App stores also may not support or enable transactions in e-CNY in their app stores."
